**Overall Meaning:** 

This (Self) is easily attainable, completely knowable, and close like a friend. It is the six-footed (being) in the cavity of the lotus (heart) of all bodies.

This verse highlights the accessibility and intimate nature of the Self. It is within everyone, residing in the heart like a six-footed insect (a metaphor for the subtle self) within a lotus flower. The verse emphasizes that the Self is always available and readily knowable, waiting to be discovered. 
